And not only that, but Bestia would not be tribune till 10 Deo„ while we are led to suppose in 36. 1-3 that Catiline had already reached Faesulae long before that date. There is therefore a general agreement among the commentatore that S. did not write Faesulanum. Dietsoh has suggested Goreuleuum (Carsulae near Narnia in Umbria) and Trossuleuum (Trossulum near Volsinii in Etruria).
